                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-613223936" class="vote-count">63</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-613223936" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="613223936">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/lonelyattic/">清汐</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-12-08</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">用书中的方法超快速地读了此书。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="442220867">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-442220867" class="vote-count">70</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-442220867" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="442220867">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/cavalier_sh/">cavalier</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar50 rating" title="力荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-04-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">这本书是为那些阅读量积累到一定程度后想要再上一个层次的&#34;阅读者&#34;准备的。从此以后，阅读将是一项专门的运动，同样需要技巧、脑力、智识多要素综合训练后养成的习惯，是一门功夫。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="849728597">
